TI  - Limited biomass recovery from gold mining in Amazonian forests
T2  - JOURNAL OF APPLIED ECOLOGY
KW  - Amazon
KW  - biomass recovery
KW  - forest recovery
KW  - forest restoration
KW  - gold mining
KW  - land use change
KW  - secondary forests
