TI  - FINANCIAL ANALYSIS OF INVESTMENTS IN FOREST CONCESSION FOR AMAZON BRAZILIAN BY DETERMINISTIC AND STOCHASTIC METHODS
T2  - CERNE
KW  - Risk analysis
KW  - Financial viability
