TI  - A Model to Patient Abandonment Prediction in the Pulmonary Rehabilitation
T2  - PROCEEDINGS OF 16TH BRAZILIAN SYMPOSIUM ON INFORMATION SYSTEMS ON DIGITAL TRANSFORMATION AND INNOVATION, SBSI 2020
KW  - Machine Learning
