TI  - Hypsipyla grandella (Lepidoptera: Pyralidae) boring Khaya ivorensis (Meliaceae) fruits and seeds in Brazil: first report
T2  - FLORIDA ENTOMOLOGIST
KW  - borer
KW  - cedar
